data.description: Nestled at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac, this sprawling ranch home offers a tranquil retreat with its expansive single-story layout! As you approach, a broad driveway leads to a welcoming entrance flanked by a large, lush yard. Enjoy the landscape and serenity while relaxing on the rocking chair front porch! Inside, the home opens into a spacious, airy living area with vaulted ceilings and large windows that provide ample natural light. Family room also offers a cozy fireplace! The open floor plan seamlessly connects the living room to a cheerful kitchen with loads of cabinets and large dining space! The home features several generously sized bedrooms, including a master suite with a double trey ceiling, walk-in closet and spacious bathroom with a double vanity. The design emphasizes comfort and ease, with a huge laundry room, ample storage, and an attached two car garage. Nearly a half acre of room to play, entertain or relax! Ideal for families or those seeking a quiet escape within a friendly neighborhood cul-de-sac! Conveniently located to I-515/Jasper and Ellijay! All your conveniences yet still a quaint mountain town setting!
